C&H® Sugar has been a staple in my kitchen ever since I was a little girl. Growing up I have fond memories of my mom baking cakes and pies with @chsugar , so I couldn’t be more thrilled to partner with them today and create Gluten Free Easter sugar cookies, just in time for the holiday!  #ad The cookies are soft and delicious, baked with love and decorated with simple yet beautiful royal icing designs that are easy to recreate at home.
The three C&H® Sugar products used in the cookies are C&H Granulated Sugar in the Easy Baking Tub, which is ideal for bakers because it’s easy to scoop, level sugar directly from the tub and store. It also has 28% less plastic than previous packaging making it a more sustainable choice. C&H® Light Brown Sugar in the zipper bag, which provides an airtight seal and keeps brown sugar moist and C&H Powdered sugar, which makes the best royal icing! If you’re looking for the perfect gluten free cookies to bake and share with loved ones this Easter Sunday, be sure to visit the link in my bio for the recipe! Here’s to making new memories with C&H® Sugar this Easter and beyond! 
.
